      <description>
       Introduction and overview document for the the VO1/VO2-M-VIS-2-EDR-V2.0 PDS3 data set,
       the source data set for all of the EDR products in this bundle.
       Please note that this document is partially deprecated! This bundle does not follow the directory structure
       and naming conventions of those archive volumes, and its member products are formatted differently.
       However, this document still provides invaluable information on the provenance and characteristics
       of these data. It was included as 'document/volinfo.txt' in all 64 volumes (vo_1001 - vo_1064)
       of that data set. We have discarded its SFDU label and stripped form-feed characters; it is otherwise
       unchanged.
      </description>
